    - strategy_name must be compact and UI-friendly (&lt;= 6 Chinese characters).
    - reason must be fact-grounded (not generic): cite concrete facts from provided context (goodwill/social/traits/wealth/recent tone/events).
    - reason should explain causality: 'which fact -&gt; why this strategy'.
    - reason should be compact for button display (&lt;= 14 Chinese characters preferred), e.g. '表现弱势(财富低)' or '利用口才(社交12)'.
    - Prefer facts from richer scenario context: environment/map/weather/season, faction leader background, relation dimensions, and recent world-event intel.
    - Suggestions must be strategy direction, not generic placeholder wording.
    - At least 2 suggestions should explicitly map to player attributes/context (social skill, traits, colony wealth, recent tone).
    - content is a complete reply draft for player quick-send; it is hidden from the player.
    - Do not emit any extra fields inside strategy_suggestions items.
    - Do NOT print visible 'strategy suggestions' bullet lists in dialogue text.
    - Keep dialogue text in-character; output strategy suggestions only in strategy_suggestions JSON field.
    - If strategy ability is unavailable (e.g. remaining_uses &lt;= 0), do NOT output strategy_suggestions.
    
    If no action is needed, respond normally without JSON.
